brightboundContext = "BrightBoundAI uses AI personalization to create and manage successful cold email campaigns on behalf of Accounting firms and CPAs in the United States (client). We find prospective customers, enrich their information, then use AI to create custom email campaigns for each prospect, and then deliver them on client's behalf, scheduling an introductory call with the qualified prospect directly in the client's calendar. Our offer is performance based, only pay for qualified prospects that show up to the call. We also offer 100% money back 30 day satisfaction guarantee."